"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"*[First Published on @IOSG Medium on Oct 14, 2020](https://medium.com/iosg-ventures/iosg-ventures-newsletter-13-fe64a0a8f0ff)*\\n\\nWelcome to our bi-weekly newsletter date from 23th September to 14th October.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ExWY4u2BNXFv58k-ko2FS.png?height=584&width=1152)\\n\\n# Announcement:\\n\\n# IOSG 7th Old Friends Reunion ‚Äî DeFi Summit 2020\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/AS5o5NFABsDg2xl2mXsdL.png?height=903&width=1400)\\n\\nLeading the future trends in DeFi. We are only 2 weeks away from the most anticipated blockchain event in 2020, featuring IOSG Ventures, Vitalik Buterin and many more! Click the link below to register ASAP.\\n\\n[https://eventbrite.hk/e/iosg-7th-old-friends-reunion-defi-summit-2020-tickets-122011376311](https://t.co/O39SNe742K?amp=1)\\n\\n# Crypto Art Gallery ‚Äî The Time of Variation\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/uISSj4IaIqnk3KQFEZfjF.png?height=383&width=680)\\n\\nAnnouncing our Crypto Art Gallery in partnership with SuperRare, ArtGee, ChainNews and Digital Renaissance, featuring Pak, Esteban Diacono, FEWOCiOUS and many more!\\n\\n# Insight:\\n\\n![Source: DevCon5(Osaka), UMA Presentation](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WSnGd4a86N-uRnZ8v1WGy.png?height=183&width=892)\\n\\nSource: DevCon5(Osaka), UMA Presentation\\n\\nUMA is a protocol for building synthetic assets. It provides smart contract templates, allowing anyone to create synthetic assets that track the price of any value subject. UMA also has its decentralized oracle system as a support.\\n\\nOverall, the UMA project consists of two core concepts: Self enforcing contract design patterns that allow remargining, and an oracle mechanism for honest price reporting with economic guarantees.\\n\\n# üê±‚ÄçüêâIndustry\\n\\n**The Radix token sale opens on October 8th, 2020 at 18:00 UTC** and will run until all tokens are sold out, or until October 22nd, 2020 at 18:00 UTC. [Read more](https://tokens.radixdlt.com/#e-radix-token-distribution)\\n\\n**Coinbase supports Balancer (BAL) and Ren (REN) at Coinbase.com** and in the Coinbase Android and iOS apps. Coinbase customers can now buy, sell, convert, send, receive, or store BAL and REN. [Read more](https://blog.coinbase.com/balancer-bal-and-ren-ren-are-now-available-on-coinbase-b498b8e9568f)\\n\\n**Plasm Network‚Äôs 2nd lockdrop has just ended with a total of 137,253** **ETH locked in 4 weeks.** [Read more](https://medium.com/stake-technologies/plasm-unveils-the-vision-of-multi-vms-scalable-smart-contract-platform-on-polkadot-and-its-tvl-for-da2e96fd6cf4)\\n\\n**MetaMask adds extended plug-in support for Web3 privacy product Mask Network.** [Read more](https://twitter.com/danfinlay/status/1311094812603330566)\\n\\n**yearn founder Andre Cronje responded to the hack of the EMN: $8m will be returned to users.** [Read more](https://twitter.com/AndreCronjeTech/status/1310763506170499072)\\n\\n**DeBank introduces DeFi‚Äôs ‚ÄúTrue Value Locked‚Äù data** to solve the DeFi double counting problem. [Read more](https://debank.com/ranking/locked_value)\\n\\n**Nexus Mutual announced NXM staking rewards,** NXM holders that stake to provide cover for tBTC minters will be rewarded by KEEP. [Read more](https://medium.com/nexus-mutual/shield-mining-is-here-85067a30ab06)\\n\\n**PieDao announced DeFi+L,** the first truly decentralized tokenized index of large-cap DeFi projects, consists of 7 DeFi assets. [Read more](https://medium.com/piedao/announcing-defi-l-12b9a9df73ca)\\n\\n**IDEX, a decentralized exchange, will launch version 2.0 on October 20**. [Read more](https://twitter.com/AlexWearn/status/1314246689386123266)\\n\\n**DeFi protocol Persistence will launch a staking airdrop campaign** that will distribute one million XPRT tokens to participants. [Read more](https://twitter.com/PersistenceOne/status/1313837629905960967)\\n\\n**Rari Capital launches Rari V2 on Oct 20 which includes liquidity mining, and governance token RGT.** [Read more](https://medium.com/rari-capital/announcing-rgt-the-long-term-yield-token-b2593502a7f3)\\n\\n# üê±‚ÄçüöÄ Our portfolio companies\\n\\n**Persistence Raises $3.7M** from Industry Heavyweights to Bridge Traditional Finance and DeFi via NFTs. [Read more](https://medium.com/persistence-blog/persistence-raises-3-7m-from-industry-heavyweights-to-bridge-traditional-finance-and-defi-via-nfts-a30256cdb428)\\n\\n**Privacy infrastructure NuCypher CEO MacLane Wilkison stated in the community that the NuCypher mainnet is scheduled to go live on October 15.** [Read more](https://blog.nucypher.com/nucypher-worklock-update/)\\n\\n**ConsenSys Codefi, a platform launched by ConsenSys that supports the institutional-level Ethereum 2.0 staking pledge service,** announced that it will help the decentralized storage project Filecoin launch its mainnet this month through the market application Filecoin Storage and the Ethereum bridge service Filecoin DeFi Bridge. [Read more](https://codefi.consensys.net/blog/consensys-codefi-to-launch-a-filecoin-defi-bridge-and-storage-market?utm_campaign=Codefi%20Activate&utm_content=141387613&utm_medium=social&utm_source=twitter&hss_channel=tw-1156973517264625665)\\n\\n**IoTeX and IoT chip manufacturer WISeKey have reached a cooperation to jointly promote trusted and safe manufacturing.** [Read more](https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/09/28/2100049/0/en/WISeKey-selected-by-IoTeX-to-Ensure-Integrity-in-Manufacturing-by-using-Secure-Semiconductors-with-Blockchain.html)\\n\\n**DODO, a decentralized trading platform, has launched DODO tokens through the first liquidity issuance.** [Read more](https://medium.com/dodoex/announcing-the-dodo-token-and-initial-dodo-offering-f31b0beb7463)\\n\\n**Aave ecological NFT platform Aavegotchi launched GHST pledge plan on Kovan testnet**, mainnet will be launched at the end of the fourth quarter. [Read more](https://testnet.aavegotchi.com/shop)\\n\\n**Synthetix officially released Biotite products, including the new Synth icon.** Through the clever combination with the Synthetix protocol, users can more clearly understand the meaning of each Synth asset. [Read more](https://blog.synthetix.io/biotite-product-release/)\\n\\n# ü¶Ñ About IOSG\\n\\nFounded in 2017, IOSG Ventures is a research and community-driven concept.we are focusing on Open Finance, Web 3.0, and cross-chain industry. We have over 60 investments and been actively involved in various developer & DAO communities. We invest in top teams with innovative ideas, operational excellence, and a robust community, and always supportive to IOSG portfolios to grow local communities in China, the US, and Germany.\\n\\nIf you would like IOSG Ventures to consider your project, please send a summary of your project along with a pitch deck and/or white paper to [hello@iosg.vc](mailto:hello@iosg.vc)\\n\\nFollow us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/IOSGVC).\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/6y7GmHYa_4oI2qlG8kvea.png?height=122&width=1037)\\n\\n \\n \",\"timestamp\":1641455471,\"title\":\"IOSG Ventures Newsletter #13\"},\"digest\":\"2AUA_yqcv0B0Ho_Z_HqP456eXDVqzmjxibVoXjBzgDc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd8159c4DD43FEe99FA86D0BAaCA7a9cC33334864\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"IrNwRyyV5qeEAVKrYYbR2GwKgwV9oiBiSE4OmxNmg_A\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"crLJpYwXR67C4ldGG508kcIM-ReUBDH5YblmiE3RDmU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"tuyDqlrlbDfCb-RMJfr7mOprVhm8Xd-cnry_qwNEYeOR2X_JnMs_qo4aEGNDjebW2pOPNSse20dmWBMBaYOoKg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3cacac780fe70792bba7704453b9c0e94a2f67fde8f900d8fb3c5673ec818826037300d7a781c78d788fd5b8f77006f8346e179822bce17f127a3557e49a5e211c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\